data.description: Open and spacious floor plan, oversized covered front porch, 4th bedroom/study has upgraded solid oak French doors & built in oak bookcase, no closet, wood laminate flooring throughout home, formal dining, kitchen island with sink that overlooks living room, fireplace with brick surround, separate garden tub and shower, double vanity, ceiling fans throughout, extended rear wood deck along back of house, on cul-de-sac street, storage shed, subdivision has park, pool, playground, basketball and volleyball court and covered pavilion for family gatherings, also walking trails that go all the way to Fairly Park and Old down town Hutto
